        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "This is some stolen ring, it seems but it didn't belong to one of our fellow Inn Keepers. I am sure of it. Well, anyway... we told them not to mess with us now, and I thank you! We should be having less troubles with them now."
