        },
        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "*Grin* Indeed. There were two assailants that attacked him. One just kept guard, while the other drew a blade and cut his arm. They obviously just wanted to scare him, and us, as they only took two rings they found, nothing else. If you find one of them, bring back a ring you might find on them so I confirm."
          }
        }
