        },
        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "They are someplace around the Shire and Bree, as usually I suppose. I will reward you the most if you get the man who attacked him, slightly less if you get his guard. We do not know what they look like, so I suppose you should just try to be lucky. Whoever you find, cut him down. We must show we can defend ourselves."
          }
